  "time_ut": 1658001890,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Politicians vie for power'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "South Sri Lankan politicians are in competition to see who will come to this power, but no one has the thought of rebuilding this country economically. District Member of Parliament D. Siddharthan said.",
        "He said this while addressing the 33rd Heroes' Day of Tamil Eelam People's Liberation Kazhagam held at Vuniya Kovilkulam yesterday (16). He further stated,",
        "This economic hardship is not new to our people. This is something that our people have already experienced.",
        "Our people have been experiencing many hardships economically and politically for a long time. Today the country is under a massive economic and political crisis. There is a situation of what will happen next.",
        "Today the country is under a massive economic and political crisis. There is a situation of what will happen next.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa's resignation from the post of President and Mahinda Rajapaksa's resignation from the post of Prime Minister have been demonstrated by these protesters through protests.",
        "He said that all the governments that came to this country since independence did not care about the economic development or the harmony of all the races, but focused their full attention on suppressing the ethnic minorities and nationalities. (a)"
      ],
